descript.abstract: Polygons depict the boundaries of Washington State's incorporated municipalities, as recorded by the Washington State Office of Financial Management. Attributes include city names as provided by the Washington State Office of Financial Management, and Federal Information Processing Standard codes(FIPS) as provided by the National Institute of Standards and Technology. The Washington State Office of Financial Management provided FIPS codes for cities incorporated after the National Institute of Standards and Technology's FIPS code publication date. GNIS (Geographic Name Information System) codes provided by the Washington State Department of Revenue have been included for this quarter.Metadata Please direct questions about this data to Kandie Rackleff, GIS Analyst – racklek@wsdot.wa.gov – (360)570-2366. If you are having trouble viewing the data, please contact our Online Map Support.
descript.purpose: Incorporated City Limits Boundaries of Washington State
